  "voice": [
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_monolog_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お姉ちゃん……ちゃんと緊張感を持ってほしいんだけど。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_monolog_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_monolog_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "す、すごかった……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_monolog_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_monolog_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "もう終わってしまうのかと……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_monolog_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_monolog_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "エイミさんですか？暑いーと言って外に出ちゃいました。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_monolog_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_monolog_5",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "まさかこんなところまで来ることになるなんて……私たち、ただのゲーム開発部なのに。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_monolog_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_select_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ぶ、無事に帰れるんでしょうか……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_select_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_select_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私たち、ゲーム開発部なのに……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_select_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_select_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ですが、みんなのお役にたてるのなら……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_select_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_select_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "さっきのゲーム、難易度が変だったような……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_select_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_carrier_select_5",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "……大丈夫ですよね。先生が、いますから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_carrier_select_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlobby_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "預言者のコアを何かに使うようですが……一体……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlobby_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ケイちゃんと会長がちゃんと説明してくれたのに……すみません。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlobby_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "会長……どこに行ってしまったんですか……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlobby_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlobby_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "どうか、みんな無事でいてくれますように……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlobby_5",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "最後まで最善を尽くします。あ、最後って言うとなんだか不吉な感じがしますね……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlobby_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlogin_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "これは、なんでしょう……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlogin_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlogin_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "おかえりなさい、先生。ここは……格納庫？みたいです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlogin_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlogin_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "アップグレードができますね！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlogin_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlogin_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生……みんな……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlogin_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlogin_5",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "（私がちゃんとしっかりしないと……！しっかり！）",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlogin_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_eventlogin_6",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "まだ全然信じられないです……どうしてこんなことに。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_eventlogin_6.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0268_r89_mainscenario_battle_10",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "つ、つまり……ネクロマンサー、みたいなものですか！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E7%BB%BF/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0268_r89_mainscenario_battle_10.ogg"
    }
  ],
